                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880402-12-off59 t17880402-12-cd60"></join> last, a side of an iron grate, value 18 d. an iron axle-tree, value 2 s. an iron and steel anvil, value 20 s. and a bar of iron, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17880402-12-victim155" type="victimName">
                  Samuel 
                  Foley
               <interp inst="t17880402-12-victim155" type="surname" value="Foley"></interp>
